{"tid":2213063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中港外媒淪籌碼 北京自毀聲譽","createTime":"2020-09-22T09:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T09:50:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1115f52f1e5cfd242d4744f0525e2458ade095ce","tid":2213063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200922/BNUPYF44CFGZRLAVZY3NSBTZD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200922%2FBNUPYF44CFGZRLAVZY3NSBTZD4%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I28orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=eab0a2cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200922%2FBNUPYF44CFGZRLAVZY3NSBTZD4%2F&h=2bd32f9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200922/BNUPYF44CFGZRLAVZY3NSBTZD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中港外媒淪籌碼 北京自毀聲譽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jmjUPiohuiioTwb28X2euBDg6Ic=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E72V4OLMQBG3XLRMPQFS2FF2YI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjmjUPiohuiioTwb28X2euBDg6Ic%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE72V4OLMQBG3XLRMPQFS2FF2YI.jpg&h=e26ddc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■卡尼14歲的女兒（中）也被指違反簽證規定，要拍片認罪。<br />\n<br />\n當本月上旬最後兩名澳洲記者緊急撤離後，駐華外國記者協會發表聲明，指單是今年上半年，中國已經驅逐了17個外媒記者。同時，在中美角力影響下，就連香港都被牽連，香港外國記者會（FCC）上月發聲明指，多名駐港外國記者被延遲發工作簽證，絕不尋常。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：揭新疆集中營黑幕 遭當局滋擾屈違法  澳記者爆中共卑鄙手段 深夜叩門 入侵手機 幼女作脅<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。《華盛頓郵報》北京分社社長亦因記者證被拒延期，上周離開中國，這也令《華郵》40年來首度沒有中國特派記者。<br />\n<br />\n駐華外國記者協會兩周前發聲明，稱兩名澳洲記者撤離後，已再沒有澳洲駐華記者；。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》記者遷往台北首爾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YtWrEqYEm1ZYc4vsGfgjLcJg1Hk=/2725x1842/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2B6ZH4M66FHZPPNP7SSGXCVVGI.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYtWrEqYEm1ZYc4vsGfgjLcJg1Hk%3D%2F2725x1842%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2B6ZH4M66FHZPPNP7SSGXCVVGI.GIF&h=b9353b02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美角力下，在港工作的外國記者也成籌碼，上月FCC發聲明，多名駐港記者被延遲發工作簽證，絕不尋常。。。。。。。。。。。，《紐約時報》已決定把部份被逐離開中國的記者遷往台北及首爾，繼續報道中國新聞。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/美國之音"},{"pid":"9cc81b429180d4071be03ab2d9d880a4263b7320","tid":2213063,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"天朝可以自設外媒代表外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大生意來"},{"pid":"4d08e372ce758a531bb5905e82903ce39097033f","tid":2213063,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc81b429180d4071be03ab2d9d880a4263b7320","tid":2213063,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"天朝可以自設外媒代表外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大生意來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"自設美國 英國 法國<br />\n證明同國際友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb42fc66e1501a3eafaae59e13330f376cab0d8","tid":2213063,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/robert_spalding/status/1308167587524743168?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frobert_spalding%2Fstatus%2F1308167587524743168%3Fs%3D20&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I28orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=40c293e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frobert_spalding%2Fstatus%2F1308167587524743168%3Fs%3D20&h=28d05964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/robert_spalding/status/1308167587524743168?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"535dcbd99b3abf84a3a5b69dba3fc4121b3e91e6"